; OCaml extraction of the quadrivalent domain.
;
; The prelude quadrivalentextract.v is compiled (in dune's DuneExtraction
; namespace) and `Separate Extraction` emits one .ml/.mli per module below.
; (mode promote) copies the generated files back into this source directory,
; so they sit next to any hand-written OCaml.
(coq.extraction
 (prelude quadrivalentextract)
 (theories RocqBottom Stdlib)
 (extracted_modules Datatypes QuadrivalentComp QuadrivalentTheory OpsComp)
 (mode promote))
